text: Xenorhabdus khoisanae is a bacterium from the genus of Xenorhabdus which has been isolated from the nematode Steinernema khoisanae in the Western Cape Province in South Africa.UniProtDeutsche Sammlung von Mikroorganismen und Zellkulturen == References == == Further reading == * * ==External links== *Type strain of Xenorhabdus khoisanae at BacDive - the Bacterial Diversity Metadatabase Category:Bacteria described in 2013
title: Xenorhabdus khoisanae
